                        <div class="profile" >
                            
                                

<img class="author-profile-picture" src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2011/08/25/R042/e3a48f6c-d8b0-4e33-b1a3-9ee55cdd2cd9/60x60.png" height="60" width="60" alt="" />
