<img class="author-profile-picture" src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2011/02/04/flatfrog/49712a18-bd71-4904-9a07-58bcc3f5994b/60x60.png" height="60" width="60" alt="" />
<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/discussion/user/flatfrog" title="User profile page">flatfrog</a>

                            
